{
  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a cityscape adorned with vibrant fireworks. A long, illuminated bridge stretches across dark water, connecting the foreground to the bright city skyline. The bridge features a series of arches and is lined with bright white lights, creating a striking visual contrast against the dark water.  Behind the bridge, the city is a tapestry of lights, with buildings of varying heights illuminated in warm yellows and oranges. Above the cityscape, a spectacular firework display explodes in a cascade of red, white, and blue bursts. The fireworks are positioned over a prominent skyscraper, highlighting its silhouette against the night sky. The overall composition blends natural elements like water and urban structures with the dynamic energy of the fireworks.",
